            . The prisoner was my <rs id="t18150405-109-deflabel590" type="occupation">second receiving clerk</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18150405-109-defend969 t18150405-109-deflabel590"></join>, his duty was to receive money, notes, and valuable securities for me, and to account them to me; he went round to collect money for me; I know the goods were sold to Mr. Bywaters, I was in the shop at the time.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18150405-109-person973">
                  NICHOLAS 
                  GOODBURN
               <interp inst="t18150405-109-person973" type="surname" value="GOODBURN"></interp>
